		<section id="H0E039231E9A14ED7BD4E4BB60268A132" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short title; table of
			 contents</header>
			<subsection id="H9679EC9D38F34A70A86B2DB8709F4D87">
        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>Short
			 title</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">This Act may be cited
			 as the <quote>
            <short-title>The Earned Income Tax Credit Improvement and
			 Simplification Act 2013</short-title>
          </quote>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="HB45F07B63F28451781C2F25925512962">
        <enum>(b)</enum>
        <header>Table of
			 contents</header>
        <text>The table of contents for this Act is as follows:</text>
				<toc container-level="legis-body-container" lowest-bolded-level="division-lowest-bolded" lowest-level="section" quoted-block="no-quoted-block" regeneration="yes-regeneration">
					<toc-entry idref="H0E039231E9A14ED7BD4E4BB60268A132" level="section">Sec. 1. Short title; table of contents.</toc-entry>
					<toc-entry idref="HD5D8EC2D63684A1C847B5534E17649FE" level="section">Sec. 2. Certain improvements in the earned income tax credit
				made permanent.</toc-entry>
					<toc-entry idref="HBCBF53C4E71248CB8B6A435502124160" level="section">Sec. 3. Strengthening the earned income tax credit for
